stimulus:
Welcome to this experiment on daily rhythms and cognition.

First you will be asked some questions about yourself.

Then a short experiment will measure your response time.

Take the test at different times of the day/night.

Press any key to begin.
How Sad/Angry or Happy are you right now?
How Tired/Sleepy or Fresh/Awake are you right now?

In this experiment, a face and a word will appear in the center of the screen.

If the face is happy, press the letter H with right index finger.

If the face is fearful, press the letter F with left index finger.

Respond as fast as possible while being correct. Ignore the written words.

Press the H key for happy faces

Press the F key for faces with fear

Press any key to begin.
